The paper focuses on the study of social spambots on Twitter, which involves analyzing collective behaviors and detecting anomalies in user behavior. This suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Sound and Music Computing (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning and data mining techniques to analyze large datasets, which could also place it under the categories of Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
